STATE of Connecticut
v.
Lisa WHITNUM-BAKER Supreme Court of Connecticut. Decided February 15, 2017

Lisa Whitnum-Baker, self-represented, in support of the petition.

Nancy L. Walker, deputy assistant state's attorney, in opposition.

The defendant's petition for certification for appeal from the Appellate Court, 169 Conn. App. 523, 150 A.3d 1174 (2016), is denied.
